## 12. Success Metrics

### 12.1 Technical Metrics
- Processing success rate: >95%
- Average processing time: <10 minutes per hour of video
- Output quality score: >8/10 average
- Error rate: <5%

### 12.2 Business Metrics
- Reduction in manual audio processing time: 80%
- Voice cloning sample acceptance rate: >90%
- Admin user satisfaction: High

## 13. Risks and Mitigation

### 13.1 Technical Risks
- **YouTube ToS Changes**: Monitor and adapt to API changes
- **Large File Processing**: Implement chunking and streaming
- **Quality Inconsistency**: Develop robust quality assessment

### 13.2 Legal/Compliance Risks
- **Copyright**: Only process content with proper permissions
- **Privacy**: Ensure secure handling of audio data
- **YouTube ToS**: Comply with download restrictions

## 14. Deliverables

### 14.1 Phase 1 (MVP)
- Core CLI tool with basic processing
- YouTube and local file support
- Eleven Labs output profile
- Basic quality assessment
- Documentation and setup instructions

### 14.2 Phase 1.5 (Enhancement)
- Batch processing capabilities
- Advanced audio cleaning
- Multiple output profiles
- Comprehensive logging and monitoring

This PRD defines a focused, achievable system that can be implemented incrementally while providing immediate value to the platform's voice cloning initiatives.